This template standardizes the **root cause drilldown workflow**.

## ğŸ“ Investigation Framework
Root cause analysis should follow this order:

1. Confirm the metric change
2. Decompose metric drivers
3. Identify segment contribution
4. Check outliers
5. Verify persistence
